    refreshRepoVisibility(): walks the active tab's shellCwd() up
    for a .git ancestor, parses [remote "origin"] url from
    .git/config (both https:// and git@ URL forms), then resolves
    visibility via `gh repo view --json visibility -q .visibility`.
