    api.github.com/repos/milnet01/ants-terminal/releases/latest via
    QNetworkAccessManager, parses tag_name, and compares against
    ANTS_VERSION via the new pure helper compareSemver. Hourly
    timer plus a 5 s singleShot on startup. Click opens the
    release page in the user's browser.
  * Added: pure helpers in mainwindow.cpp — findGitRepoRoot,
    parseGithubOriginSlug, compareSemver.
  * Tests: tests/features/github_status_bar/ — 12 invariants
    covering label declaration/construction/object-name/hidden-
