ants-terminal (0.7.42-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Inline ghost-text completion in the Command Palette — Claude
    Code's /slash-command UX, ported to Ctrl+Shift+P. As the user
    types, the unmatched suffix of the top fuzzy-match is rendered
    in a dimmed colour right after the cursor; Tab commits the
    suggestion into the input. Retires ROADMAP § "Command Palette
    ghost-completion (near-term, small scope)".
  * Added: GhostLineEdit subclass of QLineEdit (in
    src/commandpalette.h). Carries an m_ghost string set via
    setGhostSuffix(); paintEvent calls QLineEdit::paintEvent first,
    then draws the ghost at cursorRect().right() + 1 using
    palette().color(QPalette::Text) with setAlphaF(0.45). No layout
    changes — the suffix overlays the existing line-edit content
    area.
  * Added: CommandPalette::updateGhostCompletion(filter), invoked
    from populateList after the result list is rebuilt. Empty
    filter, empty list, or non-prefix top-match → empty ghost;
    case-insensitive prefix match → ghost = name.mid(filter.length())
    with action-name casing preserved. contains()-only matches get
    an empty ghost.
  * Added: Tab-key commit handler. Appends ghost to input via
    setText (preserving user-typed casing on commit, mirroring
    shell-completion semantics). Tab is always consumed so focus
    cannot leave the palette while it is open. Tab does not execute
    — the user presses Enter to run, matching Claude Code's
    /slash-completion contract.
  * Tests: tests/features/command_palette_ghost_completion/ — ten
    invariants on the GhostLineEdit type, ghost transitions across
    empty / prefix / uppercase-prefix / contains-only / no-match
    filters, Tab commit semantics, focus retention on empty-ghost
    Tab, source-grep on the dimmed-color literal and cursorRect
    anchor, and Esc dismiss regression. Drives CommandPalette
    directly under QT_QPA_PLATFORM=offscreen. Pre-fix verification:
    with the implementation stashed, the test fails to even compile
    (missing GhostLineEdit symbol).

