    non-zero-exit-with-stderr-only patterns (clang-tidy missing
    compile_commands.json). Now: parameters named, function
    branches on QProcess::CrashExit, both warnings demoted to
    Severity::Info. The four exit modes (timeout / overflow /
    crash / non-zero-with-stderr-only) funnel through a single
    makeToolHealthWarning helper. Locked by
    tests/features/audit_tool_crash_distinct (4 invariants).

