    lazy-created in show() instead of at MainWindow construction,
    so QAbstractItemView timers don't fire at idle.
  * Fixed: QMainWindow::setAnimated(false) — we have no dock
    widgets; the animator ran continuously at idle.
  * Fixed: Qt UI effect animations disabled globally
    (UI_AnimateMenu, UI_FadeMenu, UI_AnimateCombo, UI_AnimateTooltip,
    UI_FadeTooltip, UI_AnimateToolBox) via
    QApplication::setEffectEnabled.
